1.2
log
@update to teTeX 2.0.1

The long awaited update:
- lots of updates to current packages
- lots of bugfixes
- lots of new packages
- cleanup of licenses, it's all free now (GPL, LPPL, ...)

see ${PREFIX}/share/texmf/ChangeLog for details
